CatDescriptText: Related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 11, 1950, pg. 1. Headline reads: "First Baptist Church, Penn Township, Is Scene Of Ceremony Uniting Miss Gaines, Mr. Hollinger"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of three women, possibly Marjorie Ellen Gaines or Evelyn Gaines Love, Nanie B. Allen, and Mrs. Charles M. Gaines, and girl, possibly Velma Jeanne or Lorie Love, wearing light colored dresses, posed in front of dark crushed velvet curtain, for Gaines - Hollinger wedding, First Baptist Church
